Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:56.40,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背負「自由之翼」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:03.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握決意抵在左胸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:08.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}劈裂「愚行之螺旋」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.88,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}翱翔於蒼穹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自由之翼
