Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:41.41,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}如果我不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:46.37,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你還能夠說是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:51.67,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}崩壞的砂器散落一地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:57.01,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}破碎的心能否重新拾起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:23:06.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}何人的呼喚 幻化為耳鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:11.11,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}時間似乎靜止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:14.15,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}啊 覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:19.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}衝破這無邊的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:24.20,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}疾風一般逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:29.17,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}曾如行屍走肉一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:36.17,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我們 到城牆之外 再相見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:40.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}在地圖之外
